Current Question Text: What occurrence number is this? (1, 2, 3, etc)
Notes: Will be used to track the number of occurrences for participant. Initial use: cancerOccurrences. Each occurrence goes in a separate Firestore doc. This is an integer value and tracks the number of the occurrences for the specific occurrence type. Ex: If a participant has been diagnosed with cancer twice, the occurrence number would be 1 for the first diagnosis, 2 for the second. Should be for consented, verified, and not withdrawn participants only
